            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, drain then add your <strong>jumbo prawns </strong>and <strong>chopped pepper </strong>to the pan with the <strong>sliced chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> ground turmeric</strong>,<strong> curry powder</strong>, your <strong>ground allspice </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> </strong>cook for 2-3 min or until the pepper has slightly softened</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1705678178195-x200.jpg",
