            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain your <strong>pineapple</strong> and chop into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Tip: Keep the pineapple juice for your smoothies, cakes or marinades!</p><p>Trim, then finely slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1705678182068-x200.jpg",
