            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Once the pepper has slightly softened, add your<strong> chopped creamed coconut</strong>, <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong>, <strong>tomato paste </strong>and 150ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [200ml]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[250ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>to the pan</p><p>Stir it all together and cook for 4-5 min further or until the sauce is starting to thicken and the jumbo prawns are cooked through</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
